tails I’m missing that would help clear this up! Okay, so I’ll look deeper into the structure and dependencies involved with `Props`.\"}]}"}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_ySfBQ4mvpNAihSpDuLRBe61G|fc_09f812cfcbd85c080169fb2290c95481968c8b4e053df9b927", "name": "bash", "arguments": {"command": "rg -n \"object Props|case class Props|class Props\" /home/vjovanov/c/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge2/forge/local_repositories/source_context/com.typesafe.akka/akka-actor_2.13/2.8.8/main/extracted/akka/actor -S", "timeout": 20}, "partialJson": "{\"command\":\"rg -n \\\"object Props|case class Props|class Props\\\" /home/vjovanov/c/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge2/forge/local_repositories/source_context/com.typesafe.akka/akka-actor_2.13/2.8.8/main/extracted/akka/actor -S\",\"timeout\":20}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 760, "output": 1673, "cacheRead": 12800, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 15233, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1778066041004, "responseId": "resp_09f812cfcbd85c080169fb2279540c81968dad76b3d9fb8e0c"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_ySfBQ4mvpNAihSpDuLRBe61G|fc_09f812cfcbd85c080169fb2290c95481968c8b4e053df9b927", "toolName": "bash", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "/home/vjovanov/c/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge2/forge/local_repositories/source_context/com.typesafe.akka/akka-actor_2.13/2.8.8/main/extracted/akka/actor/Props.scala:22:object Props extends AbstractProps {\n/home/vjovanov/c/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge2/forge/local_repositories/source_context/com.typesafe.akka/akka-actor_2.13/2.8.8/main/extracted/akka/actor/Props.scala:114:final case class Props(deploy: Deploy, clazz: Class[_], args: immutable.Seq[Any]) {\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1778066070095}]}
